<plot>A man wakes, only to find himself inside a painted landscape - a moving Monet. The dream scape is in constant flux, nature reshapes and reforms around him, in conflict, like his desire to free himself of this surreal confinement. Will he be lost forever in this never ending fancy or disappear like a faded memory?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?159687</url></doc>
